*
         * @prop {Number|String} itemId
         * @description
         *   Holds the item id of the current detail view item.

*
         * @prop {Object} itemData
         * @description
         *   Param test values.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} isInlineEditable
         * @description
         *   Determines if this property is inline editable (usually by the widget configuration).

*
         * @private
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} testMode
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Controls whether component will assume it's in the test mode. In test mode, no requests will be made to the
         *   server, allowing for easier testing and inclusion in the design system.

*
         * @prop {Object} testContent
         * @description
         *   Param test values.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} formMode
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Indicates if the edit form is active.

*
         * @prop {String} columnLayout
         * @description
         *   The current column layout.

*
         * @prop {String} screenType
         * @description
         *   The screen type where the property is placed.

*
         * @prop {Object} content
         * @description
         *   The content passed directly to the component.

*
         * @prop {String} businessObjectType
         * @description
         *   Defines business object type.

*
         * @prop {String} businessObjectTypePath
         * @description
         *   Defines business object path to be used in URLs.

*
         * @prop {Object} params
         * @description
         *   Extra widget parameters.

*
         * @prop {Function|undefined} customColumnLayoutCols
         * @description
         *   Custom handler that returns the number of columns
         *      that the component should use.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} layout
         * @description
         * Layout to be used by the property. Possible layouts are `PropertyInline` and `PropertyPopover`.
eslint-disable-next-line max-len

*
             * @event updated
             * @description
             *   Emitted when property updated.

*
             * @event cancel
             * @description
             *   Emitted when property update is cancelled.

*
             * @event edit
             * @description
             *   Emitted when edit button is clicked.
